Class Employee

java.lang.Object
  Employee

public class Employee
extends Object

This class models an employee. The following information is maintained:

  1. the ID of the employee, an int
  2. the name of the employee, a String
  3. the salary of the employee, a double

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
iCarnegie
